title: 07/09/21 DPS Hour 1 Mike Heller
itunes:title: 07/09/21 DPS Hour 1 Mike Heller
description:
Jason Smith and Rob Parker fill in for Dan Patrick and explain why the Suns are up 2-0 on the Bucks and discuss how Milwaukee can get back into the series. Mike Heller from 1070-The Game in Madison stops by to break down the Bucks facing an 0-2 deficit and Giannis’ attempt to carry the team all by himself. Plus, have we seen the last of Trevor Bauer as a big league pitcher?
